    <span>Car Payment Calculator</span>
  </nav>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated March 2026</p>
  <h1>Car Payment Calculator</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">Estimate your monthly auto loan payment including down payment, trade-in value, sales tax, and interest. Compare loan terms from 24 to 84 months to find the right balance between monthly cost and total interest paid.</p>

  <ReviewedBy />

  <div class="calculator-box">
    <div class="calc-inputs">
